Height

Gets or sets the height of this picture.

Declaration
public int Height { get; set; }
Property Value
Type Description
System.Int32

The height of this picture, in pixels. The default value is System.Int32.MinValue, which indicates no height was specified.
Remarks

LiveJournal limits images to a maximum of 100 pixels in each dimension.

Exceptions
Type Condition
System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException

The value is greater than 100.
